 \Gamma  \ottsym{,}  \Delta  \vdash   \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \odot  \ottnt{t_{{\mathrm{2}}}}   \ottsym{:}   \ottnt{A}  \odot  \ottnt{B}   \ottsym{,}  \Phi_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \ottsym{,}  \Phi_{{\mathrm{2}}} }{%
{\ottdruleFXXparaRName}{}%
}}
